## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of these approaches in practice. Additionally, the definitions and applications of these terms can vary across different healthcare settings and regions, potentially affecting the generalizability of the findings. Further empirical research and case studies would provide a more comprehensive understanding of these approaches in diverse healthcare environments.